      "x": 200,
      "y": 100,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 160,
      "label": "核心基础设施",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000003",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 220,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 160,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "**QueryEngine**\n工具调用发起方",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000004",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 420,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 160,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "**ToolBridge**\n工具桥接层",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000005",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 620,
      "y": 120,
      "width": 160,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "**ToolRegistry**\n工具注册表",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000006",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 280,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 240,
      "label": "文件系统工具",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000007",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 200,
      "text": "**FileOps (8个)**\n- Read (readOnly)\n- Write (write)\n- Edit (write)\n- Mkdir (write)\n- Rm (destructive)\n- Glob (readOnly)\n- Grep (readOnly)\n- CopilotEdit (write)",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000008",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 270,
      "y": 280,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 120,
      "label": "Git 工具",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000009",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 280,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**Git (6个)**\n- GitLog, GitStatus\n- GitBranch, GitDiff\n- GitCommit, GitPush",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000010",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 490,
      "y": 280,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 120,
      "label": "Web 工具",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000011",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 500,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**Web (2个)**\n- WebFetch\n- WebSearch",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000012",
      "type": "group",
      "x": 710,
      "y": 280,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 120,
      "label": "Bash 工具",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000013",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 720,
      "y": 300,
      "width": 180,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**Bash (1个)**\n- Bash (destructive)\n⚠️ 最危险工具",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000014",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 270,
      "y": 420,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "**五元素协议**\n1. Name 名称\n2. Schema 模式\n3. Permissions 权限\n4. Execution 执行\n5. Rendering 渲染",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000015",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 490,
      "y": 420,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 100,
      "text": "**buildTool 工厂**\n- 防御性构造\n- Schema 验证\n- 统一接口",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000016",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 50,
      "y": 540,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**权限级别**\n- readOnly: 只读\n- write: 写入\n- destructive: 危险\n- bypass: 跳过检查",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000017",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 270,
      "y": 540,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**流式执行**\nIdle → Streaming\n→ Partial → Complete\n四阶段状态机",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000018",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 490,
      "y": 540,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "**延迟发现**\nToolSearchTool\n按需加载减少\nprompt token",
      "color": "4"
    },
    {
      "id": "0000000000000019",
      "type": "file",
      "x": 710,
      "y": 540,
      "width": 200,
      "height": 80,
      "file": "02-Tool系统/02-01-🔧-Tool系统.md",
      "color": "4"
    }
